title: HTS 8413
text: Pumps for liquids, whether or not fitted with a measuring device; liquid elevators.

title: HTS 8414
text: Air or vacuum pumps, air or other gas compressors and fans; ventilating or recycling hoods incorporating a fan.

title: HTS 8421
text: Centrifuges, including centrifugal dryers; filtering or purifying machinery and apparatus for liquids or gases.
